e="text-align:right;" ></td></tr></table><table class="pathholder" path="true"><tr><td style="text-align:left;" ></td><td class="trail_left"><a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheButcher">The Butcher</a></td><td class="trail_center" path="true"><a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Villains">Villains</a></td><td class="trail_right" path="true"><a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheCaligula">The Caligula</a></td><td  style="text-align:right;" ></td></tr></table><br/>
